===Noun===
'''parrot'''

# a type of bird, many species of which are colourful and able to [[mimic]] human speech.

====Translations====
*French: [[perroquet]] ''m''
*German: [[Papagei]] ''m''
*Italian: [[pappagallo]] ''m''
*Spanish: [[loro]] ''m''

===Transitive verb===
'''to parrot'''

# to repeat (exactly what has just been said) without necessarily showing understanding, as a parrot does.

====Translations====
*French: [[répéter]] (quelque chose) comme un perroquet
*Italian: [[ripetare]] (qualcosa) [[a pappagallo]], ripetare (qualcosa) in modo [[pappagallesco]]

